            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add your<strong> ground turmeric</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> and cook for 5-6 min further or until the onion has caramelised</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1629109752240-x200.jpg",
