            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1697123305312-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Chettinad-style paneer curry </strong>with the <strong>basmati rice </strong>and<strong> warmed naans </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
